overview:
CYLEX INTERNATIONAL is an online business conglomerate consisting of 36 websites, reaching out to 5 continents and millions of customers worldwide. The CYLEX Group came to be in 1998 and since then we strive to keep adding more features and usage to our constantly evolving network.

CYLEX took on the challenge of providing fast and simple ways in which our users can find the right service anywhere. Over the years our clients revolved around different types of media and in return we consider that businesses need to present themselves in a wider variety of segments across the world wide web.

CYLEX delivers the best online free data, at any time. Furthermore, because of the vital search engine optimization we put to work, the profile pages are usually found in major search engines in the first ten results.
